Suggestions 5
Suggestions:

Analyzing data through the third quarter of FY 2020 finds nearly all top companies continue to be denied at higher rates than in the years before Donald Trump became president and instituted more restrictive H-1B policies. 

1. My  first suggestion at this point is to wait until March of the year 2021 for the expiration of the executive order signed in June of 2020 and extended to March 2021.

2. My second suggestion is, wait for the new administration to see if Biden administration inbound. it is an open question whether Trump’s attempts at reform will survive, especially since Biden has pledged to undo many of Trump’s actions.
